Overview

Community Size: Small Town

Description

Notable NPCs

Friends:

Haeleeya - Owner of the Bath House

Harburk - Town Constible

Imdarr - Priest of Tempus at AllFaiths Shrine

Kaylessa - Owner of Swinging Sword Inn

Wyer - Friend and exadventurer to the Heroes.

Known Individuals:

Marielye - Bar Maid at Helm at Highsun

Brother Eardon – Known through Kaylessa, he asked the heroes to look into the delegations absence.

Endrith – Owner of Vallivoe’s Sundries. This Gnome is an inventor, or at least trying to be.

Imdarr – Priest of Tempus at the Allfaiths Shrine.

Lady Auldarhk – Devote of Sune at the Allfaiths Shrine.

Marielye – the young waitress at Helm at Highsun.

Stannor – Stannor was known as the town drunk when the heroes first came to town, but now the owner of Waelvur’s Wagonworks.

Bad Guys:

Ilmeth – He was the previous owner of Waelvur’s Wagonworks, but he was part of a town conspiracy and murdered visitors for his master Larocca.
